%% control-plane-flow.mmd — Option A control flow
flowchart TD
  U[User] --> UI[UI / Channel Adapter]
  UI --> IC[Intents: Intent Classifier]
  IC -->|unknown/low confidence| DENY[Deny (deny-by-default)]
  IC -->|classified| PE[Policy Engine]
  PE -->|voice + MED/HIGH| CONF[Voice confirmation required]
  PE -->|KB only| KB[KB-only response]
  PE -->|DENY| DENY
  PE -->|ALLOW tools| ALLOW[Allow Tools]
  PE -->|ALLOW_HITL| HITL[HITL required]

  ALLOW --> TA[Tool Allowlist + Registry]
  TA --> TE[Tool Executor]
  TE -->|claims.read.v1| CLAIMS[(claims.read.v1)]
  TE -->|case.create.v1 requires approvalId| CASE[(case.create.v1)]
  TE --> RA[Response Assembler]

  HITL --> APPR[Await approvalId]
  APPR --> RA

  KB --> RA
  DENY --> RA
  CONF --> RA

  RA --> AUDIT[Audit Logger]
  AUDIT --> OUT[Respond to User]

  style DENY fill:#f87171,stroke:#ef4444,stroke-width:2px
  style HITL fill:#fbbf24,stroke:#f59e0b,stroke-width:2px
  style ALLOW fill:#22c55e,stroke:#16a34a,stroke-width:2px
